Hi Guys,

Not long ago Dave posted an offer without confirming any pricing with me so I've done the same to him and ordered some new hardware.

A little background info: For some time now I have been wanting to enter the SSD market but there was just no convincing him. Dave, if you're reading this we're now selling pure SSD VPS for pennies and you know what that means? The next few weeks will be beans on toast for you!

As the deed is done, there is no time limit on this one until we sell out. Help me convince Dave SSDs are the future.

This first SSD offering of ours is going to be OpenVZ but it's worth noting that unlike an estimated 90.01% of others on this website we are NOT overselling on RAM or Disk space: it is 100% dedicated. Tun/tap is supported. NAT/connection tracking currently is not but should be coming soon. 

